<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-10-29T05:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-10-29T05:00:00-05:00" n="229" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d229">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/5520: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Tenney</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-10-29T18:00:00+08:00"><hi rend="italic">October 29,
                                        1919, 6 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received October 30, 12:36
                                p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>[From <persName corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName>:]</p>
                        <p>451. Soukine has just informed me that <persName corresp="#p_DGMK1">General Dietrichs</persName> has given instructions for the
                            Siberian Army to retreat behind the Ishim River and there make a stand.
                            Preparations are also being made in Omsk to defend the city if
                            necessary. The Government has decided transfer all the assailant [<hi rend="italic">sic</hi>] ministers and personnel of the various
                            departments to Irkutsk. <persName corresp="#p_KAAV1">Kolchak</persName>,
                            heads of the departments and ministers and the gold bullion remain in
                            Omsk. These are precautionary measures and I will keep the Department
                            promptly informed of further action. <persName corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName>.</p>
                        <closer><signed><persName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tenney</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>